show.title: Martial Divine Warrior: Awakening of the Fighting Emperor
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/FbwgYQ
show.description: A disabled heir, unknowingly carrying the reborn spirit of the mighty god Odin, suddenly becomes the most powerful man on Earth. When his father dies and the vultures circle his vast fortune, deadly attacks begin to close in. Guarded by three divine goddesses, he must battle greed, betrayal, and fate itself to protect his legacy and survive.
